{"tid":1185337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不再怕忘了買　美推超強衛生紙可撐3個月","createTime":"2019-06-04T08:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T17:50:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f746a786bd3c9065fbee7bcf098ffcafe65531f5","tid":1185337,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:17:39.000Z","msg":"廁所衛生紙總是很快用完又沒時間即時補貨？美國有業者了解消費者的苦惱，推出超級版捲筒衛生紙，號稱可讓一個人持續使用3個月。<br />\n美國千禧世代結婚生子的年齡越來越晚，獨居人口逐漸增加。P&amp;G看準市場需求，推出「Charmin永遠用不完」（Charmin Forever Roll）衛生紙。該款衛生紙份量是一般超市販售捲筒衛生紙的3倍，號稱可單人使用3個月。<br />\n該款衛生紙推出單人版及多人版，多人版直徑長達30公分，單人版直徑為22公分。由於太龐大，該款衛生紙還有特製不銹鋼架，目前推出的套組（3捲衛生紙＋不鏽鋼架）售價為29美元（約913元台幣）。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190604/640_2946192a7a4ecae8bcafada4a3785bdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190604%2F640_2946192a7a4ecae8bcafada4a3785bdc.jpg&h=57d8124c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190604/640_20c496e3a1d20be17308bd7213503e37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190604%2F640_20c496e3a1d20be17308bd7213503e37.jpg&h=60fca99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190604/1578354/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190604%2F1578354%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=0246c2d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190604%2F1578354%2F&h=eeb9f410\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190604/1578354/</a>"},{"pid":"1f7fe11d4c48fa0e3fc08a564615fcf3b9d2ea26","tid":1185337,"uid":20776,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"同公廁個啲有乜分別"},{"pid":"c89bc07f702033ca7989ebe3